channel.title: I am new to RSPS's can someone please help me
channel.description:
what all do I edit in client and source so that my server will get online (like ip wise and what files, i know about client.java and gui.java but it keeps not getting online when I edit the ips...). I am using 317
please help, I know this is the wrong section but I seriously need help, if anyone can teamviewer I would appreciate it.

item.title: I am new to RSPS's can someone please help me
item.dc:creator: @jal_knight jal knight
item.description:
@jal_knight wrote:

Your server is just that; the game. The client is what allows others to connect to it.
Im running a PI and I’ve never had to change an IP in my source files. Only in the client files.

It also could be that you have a NAT router and tbh if that’s that case I wouldnt know what to tell you.

Read full topic
